  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The prevalence of chronic pain after a thoracotomy is around 48 %. This research focuses on
      the surgical approach. The posterolateral approach is compared to the axillary approach
      especially in term of development of a chronic pain.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
